name: rooster boy
description: Boktaboli, is a small town in Bangladesh. Its main industry is brick manufacturing and agriculture(potatoes, mainly). Many of the town's men have something in common -- they work as migrant labourers in Singapore, mainly toiling in the construction industry. In 2013, I had the privilege of returning to Boktaboli with a veteran migrant worker, Salim, to witness the birth of his first child.
